MIT License

This XAgent built-in Skill is adapted from development workflow ideas in:
https://github.com/jezweb/claude-skills

The Anthropic `webapp-testing` Skill was reviewed as a high-star tool-bound reference, but its text, scripts, assets, and tool workflow are not bundled or directly adapted in this XAgent copy.

Only Markdown process guidance is bundled here. Upstream command wrappers, helper scripts, Playwright automation, package-manager commands, dev-server workflows, browser tooling, and external command behavior are not bundled in this XAgent copy.

